compose_check.stdout:
name: hbot
services:
  bot-metrics-exporter:
    command:
      - /bin/sh
      - -lc
      - python /workspace/hbot/services/monitoring/bot_metrics_exporter.py
    container_name: hbot-bot-metrics-exporter
    deploy:
      resources:
        limits:
          cpus: 0.25
          memory: "134217728"
    environment:
      EXPORTER_LOG_TAIL_LINES: "200"
      HB_DATA_ROOT: /workspace/hbot/data
      METRICS_PATH: /metrics
      METRICS_PORT: "9400"
      PYTHONPATH: /workspace/hbot
    healthcheck:
      test:
        - CMD
        - python
        - -c
        - import urllib.request; urllib.request.urlopen('http://localhost:9400/metrics')
      timeout: 10s
      interval: 30s
      retries: 3
      start_period: 10s
    image: python:3.11-slim
    logging:
      driver: json-file
      options:
        max-file: "5"
        max-size: 50m
    networks:
      monitoring: null
    restart: unless-stopped
    volumes:
      - type: bind
        source: F:\Environement\git-repo\hummingbot_custo\hbot
        target: /workspace/hbot
        read_only: true
        bind: {}
  bot1:
    container_name: hbot-bot1
    deploy:
      resources:
        limits:
          cpus: 1
          memory: "1073741824"
        reservations:
          cpus: 0.25
          memory: "268435456"
    environment:
      BOT_POLICY_MODE: live
      BOT_POLICY_ROLE: live_microcap_primary
      BOT_POLICY_VERSION: multi_bot_policy_v1
      BUS_SOFT_PAUSE_ON_OUTAGE: "true"
      CONFIG_PASSWORD: ***redacted-secret***
      EVENT_POLL_MS: "1000"
      EXT_SIGNAL_RISK_ENABLED: "false"
      REDIS_CONSUMER_GROUP: hb_group_v1
      REDIS_DB: "0"
      REDIS_HOST: redis
      REDIS_PASSWORD: ""
      REDIS_PORT: "6379"
      TZ: UTC
    image: hummingbot/hummingbot:version-2.12.1
    logging:
      driver: json-file
      options:
        max-file: "5"
        max-size: 50m
    networks:
      trading: null
    restart: unless-stopped
    stdin_open: true
    tty: true
    volumes:
      - type: bind
        source: F:\Environement\git-repo\hummingbot_custo\hbot\data\bot1\conf
        target: /home/hummingbot/conf
        bind: {}
      - type: bind
        source: F:\Environement\git-repo\hummingbot_custo\hbot\data\bot1\logs
        target: /home/hummingbot/logs
        bind: {}
      - type: bind
        source: F:\Environement\git-repo\hummingbot_custo\hbot\data\bot1\data
        target: /home/hummingbot/data
        bind: {}
      - type: bind
        source: F:\Environement\git-repo\hummingbot_custo\hbot\data\bot1\scripts
        target: /home/hummingbot/custom_scripts
        bind: {}
      - type: bind
        source: F:\Environement\git-repo\hummingbot_custo\hbot\scripts\shared\v2_with_controllers.py
        target: /home/hummingbot/scripts/v2_with_controllers.py
        read_only: true
        bind: {}
      - type: bind
        source: F:\Environement\git-repo\hummingbot_custo\hbot\data\bot1\pmm_scripts
        target: /home/hummingbot/pmm_scripts
        bind: {}
      -
